' for 'ሥ' and the semantic context implied by 'የጾርዓውያን'.\n- 'የጾርዓውያን' was corrected to 'የሥርዓታውያን' (of the disciplined/people of order) for the same reason.\n- 'የጾፋም' was corrected to 'የጸፍም' (of a wall also), assuming 'ጸፍ' (wall/side) as the most plausible noun given the 'የ' prefix and 'ም' suffix.\n- 'የፁገር' was corrected to 'የጽጉር' (of hair), identifying 'ፁ' as a likely misread of 'ጽ' and 'ጽጉር' as a common noun.\n\nSplitting Protocol:\n- The conjunction 'ና' (and) was kept attached to words like 'የጾማቸውንና', 'የጾምና', 'የፀለዩበትና', 'የፀጸጥታና', and 'የፃፈውንና'. This decision adheres to Protocol 7 (Size Constraint), which would discard 'ና' if it were split as a single-character word. Amharic morphology often integrates 'ና' as a suffix, making it a valid part of the word in these contexts.\n\nLemmatization and POS Tagging:\n- For words functioning as relative clauses (e.g., 'የፀለዩበትና', 'የፀለይኩበት', 'የፃፈች'), the infinitive form of the main verb was identified as the root, and the POS was tagged as 'Verb (Relative Clause)' to reflect their grammatical function.","input_words":["የጽፎናውያን","የጾለት","የጾሙን","የጾማቸውንና","የጾምና","የጾርዓ","የጾርዓውያን","የጾታንም","የጾፋም","የፀሀፊዎች","የፀሃፊዎቹ","የፀሃፊዎች","የፀለዩበትና","የፀለይኩበት","የፀረተባይ","የፀበልተኞችን","የፀነሰቻቸውም","የፀነስሁት","የፀደው","የፀጋየ","የፀጸጥታና","የፁገር","የፃቫና","የፃፈች","የፃፈውንና","የፃፍኳቸውን","የፅብዖንን","የፅንስን","የፆምሪ","የፈለገነው"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"18d5be81-2d81-4920-b156-e767f0df05af","created_at":"2026-03-02T15:47:38.446537+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_25/chunk_0436.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Verb","root":"መፈተሽ","word":"የፈተሽኩበት","synonyms":["examine","check","inspect","test","scrutinize"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መፈተሽ","word":"የፈተሿቸው","synonyms":["examine","check","inspect","test","scrutinize"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መፈተን","word":"የፈተነበት","synonyms":["test","examine","try","prove","tempt"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መፈተን","word":"የፈተኑበት","synonyms":["test","exa